 Page+Step 5: Generators (Threshold Patterns)

  - M-CLUSTER: Random clumping - tight bunches with gaps

  Page+Step 6: Note Patterns (Note Index)
- ACT: Evenly distribute all active stages (Rise/Fall/Both)
  - RISE: Evenly distribute only Rise stages
  - FALL: Evenly distribute only Fall stages
  - BOTH: Evenly distribute only Both stages
  - NORM: Normalize threshold spacing (equal gaps)



  Page+Step 6: Transform
 - FLIP: Cycle directions (Rise→Fall→Both→Off→Rise)
  - T-MIRR: Mirror thresholds around midpoint
  - T-REV: Reverse threshold order
  - N-MIRR: Mirror note indices
  - N-REV: Reverse note order


