  Page+Step 5: Rhythm Generators

  - EUCL: Euclidean rhythm (F1: steps, F2: pulses, F3: rotation)
  - CLAVE: Classic patterns (Son/Rumba/Bossa/Bembe)
  - TUPLET: Subdivide into tuplets (F1: 3/5/7)
  - POLY: Polyrhythmic subdivision
  - M-RHY: Random generative rhythm

  Page+Step 6: Waveforms ()
